label: farmerID
comment: The unique farmer identification number or ID corresponding to this observation.

label: kisanNumber
comment: The registration number of a farmer for the PM Kisan Samman Nidhi scheme.

label: personnelInfo
comment: Personnel information of an individual or business corresponding to this observation.

label: landParcelInfo
comment: Land parcel information corresponding to this observation

label: capitalInfo
comment: The income and expenditure information corresponding to the entity.

label: schemeInfo
comment: Farmer welfare schemes information corresponding to this observation.

label: cropSpeciesInfo
comment: Information of crops corresponding to this observation.

label: extensionWorker
comment: Details about extension worker who is a trained professional and acts as facilitator, educator, and adviser, working closely with farmers to improve agricultural productivity, sustainability, and overall livelihoods

label: contactPointInfo
comment: Contact point information of a business/service corresponding to this observation

label: localeInfo
comment: Locale information corresponding to this observation.

label: landHolding
comment: The aggregate land possession attributed to a farmer.

label: language
comment: Represents the language(s) that can be used for communicating with an entity or those offered by a service corresponding to this observation.
